Package: glyfun
Title: Glycan-Centric Functional Enrichment Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Bin", "Fu", , "23110220018@m.fudan.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8567-2997"))
Description: Provides glycan-centric functional enrichment for glycoproteomics,
    moving beyond general protein-level descriptions. Instead of asking
    "Which functions are enriched in dysregulated glycoproteins?", glyfun
    enables asking "Which functions are enriched in proteins with dysregulated
    core-fucosylation?" This higher specificity delivers deeper insights by
    focusing on distinct glycan motifs to pinpoint the functional relevance of
    specific glycosylation changes. Integrates seamlessly with 'glydet' (for
    site-specific derived traits and motif quantification) and 'glystats' (for
    differential expression analysis).
